{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Control.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ControlLifter.restoreCont\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">ControlLifter</span>.<span class=\"name\">restoreCont</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Control.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ControlLifter\">ControlLifter</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\">DoElemCont</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Control.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ControlLifter.restoreCont","kind":"def","line":268,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.ControlLifter.restoreCont","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/00659f8e6071d7e46131ed643bf8003b99b044e9/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Control.lean#L268-L269"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Control.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ControlLifter.lift\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">ControlLifter</span>.<span class=\"name\">lift</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Control.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ControlLifter\">ControlLifter</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">elabElem</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\">DoElemCont</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"This function is like `MonadControl.liftWith fun runInBase => elabElem (runInBase pure)`.\nAll continuations should be thought of as wrapped in `runInBase`, so that their effects are embedded\nin the terminal `stM m (t m)` result type. This wrapping will be realized by\n`ControlStack.synthesizeConts`, after we know what the transformer stack `t` looks like.\nWhat `t` looks like depends on whether reassignments, early `return`, `break` and `continue` are\nused, considering *all* the use sites of `ControlLifter.lift`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Control.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ControlLifter.lift","kind":"def","line":239,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.ControlLifter.lift","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/00659f8e6071d7e46131ed643bf8003b99b044e9/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Control.lean#L239-L266"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Control.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ControlLifter.ofCont\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">ControlLifter</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofCont</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">info</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/InferControlInfo.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ControlInfo\">ControlInfo</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">dec</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\">DoElemCont</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab